    <h1>
     More on balancing Pistons
    </h1>
    <p>
     Posted by Mike West
    </p>
   </header>
   <div class="nav">
    <a href="/~keen/west/darkness.html">
     ‚Üê Back to Pushing Back the Darkness
    </a>
   </div>
   <dl class="meta">
    <dt>Date</dt>
    <dd>Wed, 11 Dec 1996 21:20:59 -0800</dd>
